1
00:00:08,767 --> 00:00:13,467
[GENTLE MUSIC PLAYING]

2
00:00:13,467 --> 00:00:15,433
Valentine's Day is
about spreading love,

3
00:00:15,433 --> 00:00:17,767
not just to couples,
to everyone.

4
00:00:17,767 --> 00:00:22,133
It's like a virus, but
with glitter and consent.

5
00:00:22,133 --> 00:00:23,733
[DOCTOR] Help!

6
00:00:25,433 --> 00:00:26,600
[NED] I'm going
to get you, witch!

7
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:29,167
I really hate working
on this floor!

8
00:00:29,667 --> 00:00:31,667
Spread love, Mr. Ned!

9
00:00:31,667 --> 00:00:32,833
Oh, calm down, Ned!

10
00:00:32,833 --> 00:00:35,367
The only thing you
ever caught is syphilis!

11
00:00:35,400 --> 00:00:37,333
Yes, babe, I promise I got you

12
00:00:37,333 --> 00:00:39,300
something really nice
for Valentine's Day.

13
00:00:39,300 --> 00:00:40,633
[COURIER] Oh, delivery.

14
00:00:40,633 --> 00:00:41,733
Thank you.

15
00:00:43,233 --> 00:00:44,533
Let me guess.

16
00:00:44,533 --> 00:00:46,133
Boyfriend's pearls?

17
00:00:46,133 --> 00:00:47,267
They're for my girlfriend.

18
00:00:47,267 --> 00:00:50,067
I'm working a double shift,
so I had them sent here.

19
00:00:50,067 --> 00:00:51,233
Is that Mr. Ned?

20
00:00:51,233 --> 00:00:53,467
He's always saying he likes
my gorgeous blonde locks.

21
00:00:53,467 --> 00:00:56,067
Meth makes everything
seem natural!

22
00:00:56,067 --> 00:00:57,600
[DONDON SIGHS] It's packed.

23
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:59,133
Overflow?

24
00:00:59,133 --> 00:01:00,267
Again?

25
00:01:00,467 --> 00:01:02,167
Hi, Mr. Ned!

26
00:01:03,433 --> 00:01:05,267
[MOUTHING] Sorry.

27
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:07,433
Gorgeous.

28
00:01:07,467 --> 00:01:08,467
Yeah.

29
00:01:10,067 --> 00:01:11,467
I don't want those
flowers shedding

30
00:01:11,467 --> 00:01:13,433
on the nurses' station, George.

31
00:01:13,633 --> 00:01:16,300
[NOA] Hey, guys!
A little help, please?

32
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:18,400
- [NED SNARLING]
- [DONDON] No, Mr. Walker! Bad!

33
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:20,400
[DONDON] Get down! No!

34
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:24,733
[FUNKY MUSIC PLAYING]

35
00:01:27,633 --> 00:01:30,233
[UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYING]

36
00:01:30,233 --> 00:01:32,333
[TESS YAWNING]

37
00:01:34,067 --> 00:01:37,367
Are you dating that guy
with the lazy eye again?

38
00:01:37,367 --> 00:01:40,767
I wasn't sure if he was looking
at my face or my chest.

39
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:43,167
Ew, Mom! No!

40
00:01:43,167 --> 00:01:44,467
That was in nursing school.

41
00:01:44,467 --> 00:01:47,167
He was the only one who
gave you flowers before.

42
00:01:47,167 --> 00:01:48,867
So I thought...

43
00:01:48,867 --> 00:01:51,567
Wait, who gave that?

44
00:01:51,567 --> 00:01:52,567
Nobody.

45
00:01:52,567 --> 00:01:54,167
You better tell me.

46
00:01:54,167 --> 00:01:55,567
[NOA] No one!

47
00:01:55,567 --> 00:01:58,700
Then why didn't you
put it in your office?

48
00:01:58,700 --> 00:02:00,833
Why are you hiding it here?

49
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:09,300
<i> Here, put this somewhere
before it ends in the dumpster.</i>

50
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,100
<i> Hm!</i>

51
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:12,133
<i>- Where?
- In your butthole!</i>

52
00:02:12,133 --> 00:02:13,267
<i> Figure it out!</i>

53
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:16,400
- [NOA GROANING]
<i> - No, no, no!</i>

54
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:20,167
<i> Ros, can you call security?</i>

55
00:02:20,167 --> 00:02:22,167
<i>Bigfoot has a higher chance
of showing up.</i>

56
00:02:22,167 --> 00:02:23,533
<i> You want me to page him too?</i>

57
00:02:25,233 --> 00:02:27,400
<i> Oh, cute flowers.</i>

58
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:34,367
[SOFT MUSIC PLAYING]

59
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,633
[TESS SCOFFS]

60
00:02:50,267 --> 00:02:52,667
I'm gonna kill him.

61
00:02:52,667 --> 00:02:56,900
[QUIRKY MUSIC PLAYING]

62
00:02:56,900 --> 00:03:01,233
- [GRIM CHUCKLING]
- [TRICKLING]

63
00:03:01,233 --> 00:03:05,600
Why did you give my daughter
flowers and cake?

64
00:03:07,233 --> 00:03:08,733
[GRIM SCOFFS]

65
00:03:08,733 --> 00:03:11,667
I can stand being in this body.

66
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:16,133
But I cannot conduct such a
vulgar function while you stare.

67
00:03:16,633 --> 00:03:19,200
Oh, are you insecure?

68
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:21,833
Go away!

69
00:03:22,567 --> 00:03:25,833
And stop messing
with my daughter!

70
00:03:25,833 --> 00:03:27,667
[WATER RUNNING]

71
00:03:27,667 --> 00:03:29,400
[GRIM] I guess I can do that.

72
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,967
Will you come with me then?

73
00:03:30,967 --> 00:03:34,533
Don't you have any
other spirit you can annoy?

74
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:38,567
Death is a department, Tess,
not a one-man show.

75
00:03:38,567 --> 00:03:39,700
[TESS] Fine.

76
00:03:39,700 --> 00:03:44,400
Then I open my mouth and
I tell Noa and you're done.

77
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,867
Oh, you will do no such thing.

78
00:03:46,867 --> 00:03:48,367
Watch me.

79
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,800
- [SNAPS]
- [ENERGY BURSTING]

80
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,333
[TESS EXHALES SHARPLY]

81
00:03:52,333 --> 00:03:53,733
What did you just do?

82
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:58,567
[SIGHS] Look, I may not be able
to control free will...

83
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,933
But I can make things
even harder for the dead.

84
00:04:03,433 --> 00:04:05,733
What were you going
to say again?

85
00:04:05,733 --> 00:04:08,300
I'm gonna tell Noa
that you're a...

86
00:04:08,833 --> 00:04:09,933
You're nothing but a...

87
00:04:11,967 --> 00:04:12,967
Yeah.

88
00:04:12,967 --> 00:04:14,667
I thought so.

89
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,933
[EXHALES SHARPLY]

90
00:04:24,967 --> 00:04:26,633
[ATZIN] (In Spanish)
<i> I’m here as your translator,</i>

91
00:04:26,633 --> 00:04:30,300
