proper information.

92
00:04:31,833 --> 00:04:35,900
The doctor diagnosed you with
Takotsubo Cardiomyopathy.

93
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:37,833
(In Spanish) What’s that?

94
00:04:37,833 --> 00:04:41,500
It’s a heart condition
called Takotsubo.

95
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:44,900
Otherwise known as
Heartbreak Syndrome.

96
00:04:44,900 --> 00:04:46,433
That's a thing?

97
00:04:46,967 --> 00:04:50,967
(In Spanish) Give me a second,
I'll Google it first.

98
00:04:50,967 --> 00:04:52,900
Listen.

99
00:04:52,900 --> 00:04:57,467
This reminds me of the time
when I had a heartbreak.

100
00:04:58,500 --> 00:05:01,567
I missed an audition
for Brillante Mendoza.

101
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:04,533
It's not even my fault
that I was late.

102
00:05:04,533 --> 00:05:07,433
My assistant got me
the wrong shade of foundation.

103
00:05:07,933 --> 00:05:10,800
I couldn't make myself appear
looking like that!

104
00:05:12,833 --> 00:05:13,967
I fired her.

105
00:05:15,033 --> 00:05:19,700
My heart healed,
and my pores tightened.

106
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:22,500
- Instantly.
- [CHUCKLES SOFTLY]

107
00:05:23,967 --> 00:05:25,033
Go on.

108
00:05:26,367 --> 00:05:27,900
I thought
I could understand English,

109
00:05:27,900 --> 00:05:30,000
but I have no clue
what she’s saying.

110
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:33,733
Uh, she escaped from somewhere.

111
00:05:34,767 --> 00:05:36,900
Let me get you a real nurse.

112
00:05:38,033 --> 00:05:43,300
[QUIRKY MUSIC PLAYING]

113
