[TELEPHONE RINGING]

114
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:01,367
Where--

115
00:06:01,367 --> 00:06:05,633
Hey, has anybody seen
my Valentine's Day gifts?

116
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,800
