Or the trash.

117
00:06:09,567 --> 00:06:13,733
But it's V-Day, who would just
throw away presents like that?

118
00:06:13,733 --> 00:06:14,700
Ros.

119
00:06:16,133 --> 00:06:19,733
[PHONE BUZZING]

120
00:06:19,733 --> 00:06:20,767
[GEORGE] Oh, I'm dead.

121
00:06:20,767 --> 00:06:21,900
[PHONE BUZZING]

122
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:23,467
Like, I'm actually dead.

123
00:06:23,467 --> 00:06:28,000
[PHONE BUZZING]

124
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:31,633
[QUIRKY MUSIC PLAYING]

125
00:06:33,700 --> 00:06:34,667
[COVER THUDS]

126
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:40,767
[SOFT MUSIC PLAYING]

127
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:43,367
[NOA SNIFFS DEEPLY]

128
00:06:45,433 --> 00:06:46,633
[COVER THUDS]

129
