130
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:54,533
[VASE RATTLING]

131
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:59,000
Just flowers and cake, and
you're already head over heels?

132
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,400
How pitiful.

133
