What? It's Mango Supreme,
your favorite.

134
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,633
It's a gift.

135
00:07:05,633 --> 00:07:07,900
- Normal people do that.
- Normal?

136
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:10,533
I mean, he is a bit younger
than me.

137
00:07:10,533 --> 00:07:11,833
Younger? Ha!

138
00:07:12,833 --> 00:07:13,967
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

139
00:07:14,967 --> 00:07:16,133
[DOOR KNOB CLICKS OPEN]

140
00:07:16,133 --> 00:07:17,733
You wanted to see me?

141
00:07:17,733 --> 00:07:20,433
Yeah! I wanted to thank you
for those.

142
00:07:20,433 --> 00:07:24,533
- My God, Noa, he's--
- Oh, so you think--

143
00:07:24,533 --> 00:07:28,067
