- Don't!

146
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:34,600
My treat as a thank you.

147
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,500
Yeah, sure!

148
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:38,067
Okay.

149
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:39,967
[TESS SCOFFS]

150
00:07:40,767 --> 00:07:42,133
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

151
00:07:42,133 --> 00:07:44,733
[FOOTSTEPS RETREATING]

152
00:07:45,733 --> 00:07:46,900
Lol-lol-lol-lol.

153
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:50,500
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

154
00:07:51,633 --> 00:07:55,933
