155
00:07:55,933 --> 00:07:56,867
Ros?

156
00:07:58,733 --> 00:08:00,567
Uh, where are my flowers?

157
00:08:01,100 --> 00:08:04,533
- How should I know?
- They said you threw them out.

158
00:08:04,533 --> 00:08:05,567
[WHEELS SCREECH]

159
00:08:09,500 --> 00:08:10,767
Who said that?

160
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,600
Tell me.

161
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:17,800
Or I'm going to stuff you
in that plastic bag,

162
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:20,767
