are you two spreading?

167
00:08:37,033 --> 00:08:38,167
Ros?

168
00:08:38,167 --> 00:08:40,967
- What's going on?
- Nothing, Doc.

169
00:08:40,967 --> 00:08:44,133
Only one thing I really hate
more than this dumb holiday...

170
00:08:45,633 --> 00:08:49,167
