171
00:08:49,167 --> 00:08:51,567
Dang, lady,
who broke your heart?

172
00:08:53,633 --> 00:08:57,133
She's serious, guys.
You better speak up.

173
00:08:57,167 --> 00:09:00,833
N-No, I swear, Ros.
Nothing about you.

174
00:09:00,833 --> 00:09:01,800
[ROS GROWLING]

175
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,867
Say it!

176
00:09:02,867 --> 00:09:05,167
Flowers, Noa, lunch. Together.

177
00:09:05,167 --> 00:09:06,633
[ROSS GROWLING]

178
00:09:06,633 --> 00:09:07,967
We swear!

179
00:09:07,967 --> 00:09:09,667
We only heard it
in the break room.

180
00:09:10,267 --> 00:09:12,200
- From someone else.
- Who?!

181
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,267
[GRIM EXHALES]

182
00:09:16,967 --> 00:09:19,100
