This is delicious.

187
00:09:37,167 --> 00:09:39,033
[GRIM CHUCKLING]

188
00:09:39,033 --> 00:09:40,167
[NOA CHUCKLES AWKWARDLY]

189
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,633
Um...

190
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:48,233
I know I said it was my treat,
but 50 dollars?

191
00:09:49,767 --> 00:09:51,167
That's a lot for lunch.

192
00:09:51,167 --> 00:09:52,867
[NOA CHUCKLES AWKWARDLY]

193
00:09:52,867 --> 00:09:53,833
