198
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:02,600
That's so funny.

199
00:10:02,633 --> 00:10:06,267
[GRIM GROANING]

200
00:10:06,267 --> 00:10:09,567
So, I hate secrets,
and not knowing stuff.

201
00:10:10,267 --> 00:10:11,867
- So...
- Yeah?

202
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:15,033
Tell me about yourself, Grim.

203
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:19,000
Like, why did your parents
name you that?

204
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:21,200
Sounds kind of deathly.

205
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:24,067
[QUIRKY MUSIC CONTINUES]

206
00:10:24,067 --> 00:10:25,267
Yeah.

207
00:10:25,267 --> 00:10:26,733
I have many names.

208
00:10:26,733 --> 00:10:28,267
[GRIM CHUCKLING]

209
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:32,700
[DONDON] So, basically,
the heart gets like

210
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:35,133
super sad or whatever,
and the left ventricle weakens.

211
00:10:35,167 --> 00:10:36,367
See? I'm smart.

212
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:40,767
- What broke your heart?
- Oh, no, I'm not--

213
00:10:40,767 --> 00:10:42,367
I dated a guy
without a profile pic.

214
00:10:43,067 --> 00:10:43,933
Not you.

215
00:10:43,933 --> 00:10:46,633
I regret involving
her too, sorry.

216
00:10:48,267 --> 00:10:49,967
[CAMILLE] So, you can
tell us anything.

217
00:10:49,967 --> 00:10:52,800
It's not like you're in a gossip
