218
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:56,200
You know, I stopped doing that
years ago--

219
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,867
Mostly.

220
00:10:57,867 --> 00:10:59,867
- You can tell us.
- Uh...

221
00:11:00,667 --> 00:11:02,033
My boyfriend...

222
00:11:02,967 --> 00:11:03,933
of 15 years...

223
00:11:04,733 --> 00:11:05,700
Um...

224
00:11:06,333 --> 00:11:08,000
I met him yesterday.

225
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:11,200
- She says that--
- No, no, I know that word.

226
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:14,733
"Novio" means party.
Or is that the conjugation?

227
00:11:14,733 --> 00:11:17,900
It actually means boyfriend,
but yeah, close, whatever.

228
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:19,433
[CAMILLE] You know,
when I headlined

229
00:11:19,433 --> 00:11:23,367
that Saturday teen sketch
show, Bulilit...

230
00:11:23,367 --> 00:11:26,333
I had no heartbreak.
I didn't experience that

231
00:11:26,333 --> 00:11:30,233
